出征相对便利，可以最大限度地减轻舟车劳顿对全队带来的影响。虽然客战「太极虎」取分难度不小，但一旦在中泰之战出现闪失，中国队还是需要为争夺小组出线权的最后机会做足准备。国足重回福地！世预赛将在沈阳迎战泰国队"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8fc4c0e25828e7c2001b8fbd2b5f1dec_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652016546"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0+q4+rS8ur5mEAMaCTEwNzE3MDA1MiC1/sewBjAAODBAEnIJNjUyMDE2NTQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1712675062.908825", "card_id": "Q_652198894", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在你的眼中，宁波的春天哪里最迷人？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "宁波鄞州横溪镇联合知乎城市宁波发起「乡旅共富 花香宁波」横溪寻春开游仪式，与大家分享宁波的春天。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-05267b0d46a6ae1ee03db1efc57dcac2_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/652198894"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0+q4+rS8ur5mEAMaCTEwNzIxMDUzOSDB/c2wBjAAOEZAE3IJNjUyMTk4ODk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1712675062.909860", "card_id": "Q_652226487", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "浙江 34 岁律师遇歹徒袭击身亡，律所回应非业务原因，案件进展如何，释放了什么警示信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "浙江人地律师事务所 8 日发布讣告，全文如下： 4 月 8 日，浙江人地律师事务所发布讣告：本所青年律师孙沪同志于 2024 年 4 月 6 日遇歹徒袭击，于 4 月 8 日凌晨 2 时抢救无效，不幸逝世，终年 34 周岁。 据浙江人地律师事务所官网显示，孙沪的专业领域为公司、金融、合同、建筑房地产、民商事诉讼 / 仲裁。律所发讣告：34 岁律师被歹徒袭击身亡"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5b0d3241f978d4c80bbda8886db0857b_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D"